        com.amazonaws.services.kms.AWSKMS getClient(String regionName)
        Supplies an AWSKMS instance to use for a given region. The KmsMasterKeyProvider will not cache the result of this function.
        Parameters:
        regionName - The region to get a client for
        Returns:
